{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857376501,"sessionID":"ses_286a72e99ffefKKmBHNmlIKUHY","part":{"id":"prt_d79591902001Z7afJbSVOh3h8o","messageID":"msg_d795909be001e8k5df4TKHZKme","sessionID":"ses_286a72e99ffefKKmBHNmlIKUHY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5d68706044a0478794b67414f1ef3f80","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 实现 Redis 存储后端，提供高性能的会话持久化能力。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: ```\n20: ┌─────────────────┐\n21: │ Session Manager │\n22: └────────┬────────┘\n23:          │\n24:          v\n25: ┌─────────────────┐\n26: │ SessionStore    │  (Interface - AR-012)\n27: └────────┬────────┘\n28:          │\n29:          v\n30: ┌─────────────────┐\n31: │RedisSessionStore│  (Implementation - AR-013)\n32: └────────┬────────┘\n33:          │\n34:          v\n35: ┌─────────────────┐\n36: │  go-redis/v9    │\n37: └────────┬────────┘\n38:          │\n39:          v\n40: ┌─────────────────┐\n41: │     Redis       │\n42: └─────────────────┘\n43: ```\n44: \n45: ### Dependencies\n46: \n47: | Package | Purpose |\n48: |---------|---------|\n49: | `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | Redis 客户端 |\n50: | `context` | 操作上下文 |\n51: | `encoding/json` | Session 序列化 |\n52: | `time` | 时间处理 |\n53: \n54: ## Data Structures\n55: \n56: ### RedisConfig\n57: \n58: ```go\n59: type RedisConfig struct {\n60:     Addr         string        // Redis 地址\n61:     Password     string        // 密码\n62:     DB           int           // 数据库\n63:     PoolSize     int           // 连接池大小\n64:     MinIdleConns int           // 最小空闲连接\n65:     MaxRetries   int           // 最大重试次数\n66:     DialTimeout  time.Duration // 连接超时\n67:     ReadTimeout  time.Duration // 读超时\n68:     WriteTimeout time.Duration // 写超时\n69: }\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ### RedisSessionStore\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: type RedisSessionStore struct {\n76:     client *redis.Client\n77:     config *RedisConfig\n78: }\n79: ```\n80: \n81: ## API Contracts\n82: \n83: ### Constructor\n84: \n85: ```go\n86: func NewRedisSessionStore(cfg *RedisConfig) (*RedisSessionStore, error)\n87: ```\n88: - Input: RedisConfig 指针\n89: - Output: RedisSessionStore 实例，error\n90: \n91: ### SessionStore Interface Methods\n92: \n93: #### Create\n94: \n95: ```go\n96: func (s *RedisSessionStore) Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n97: ```\n98: - Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n99: - 使用 HSET 存储 Session 字段\n100: - 设置过期时间: EXPIREAT session.ExpiresAt\n101: \n102: #### Get\n103: \n104: ```go\n105: func (s *RedisSessionStore) Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n106: ```\n107: - Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n108: - 使用 HGETALL 获取所有字段\n109: - 返回 SessionNotFoundError 如果不存在\n110: \n111: #### Update\n112: \n113: ```go\n114: func (s *RedisSessionStore) Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n115: ```\n116: - Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n117: - 使用 HSET 更新字段\n118: - 更新 UpdatedAt 时间戳\n119: \n120: #### Delete\n121: \n122: ```go\n123: func (s *RedisSessionStore) Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n124: ```\n125: - Key: `session:{sessionID}`\n126: - 使用 DEL 删除 key\n127: \n128: #### List\n129: \n130: ```go\n131: func (s *RedisSessionStore) List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n132: ```\n133: - 使用 SCAN 遍历 `session:*` keys\n134: - 根据 filter 过滤结果\n135: - 注意: 大量数据时需要分页\n136: \n137: ## Error Handling\n138: \n139: ### Custom Errors\n140: \n141: ```go\n142: var (\n143:     ErrRedisNotConnected = errors.New(\"redis: not connected\")\n144:     ErrSessionNotFound   = errors.New(\"session: not found\")\n145:     ErrInvalidConfig     = errors.New(\"redis: invalid config\")\n146: )\n147: ```\n148: \n149: ### Error Wrapping\n150: \n151: ```go\n152: if err := s.client.Get(ctx, key).Err(); err == redis.Nil {\n153:     return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"get session %s: %w\", sessionID, ErrSessionNotFound)\n154: }\n155: ```\n156: \n157: ## Redis Key Design\n158: \n159: | Key Pattern | Type | TTL | Description |\n160: |-------------|------|-----|-------------|\n161: | `session:{id}` | Hash | ExpiresAt - now | Session 数据 |\n162: \n163: ### Session Hash Fields\n164: \n165: ```\n166: session:abc123\n167:   id:           \"abc123\"\n168:   sandboxId:    \"sb-456\"\n169:   namespace:    \"default\"\n170:   name:         \"session-name\"\n171:   status:       \"active\"\n172:   createdAt:    \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n173:   updatedAt:    \"2024-01-01T01:00:00Z\"\n174:   expiresAt:    \"2024-01-02T00:00:00Z\"\n175:   lastActiveAt: \"2024-01-01T01:30:00Z\"\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ## Testing Strategy\n179: \n180: ### Unit Tests\n181: \n182: | Test Category | Coverage |\n183: |---------------|----------|\n184: | Create | 创建 session 并验证存储 |\n185: | Get | 获取存在的 session |\n186: | Get (not found) | 获取不存在的 session |\n187: | Update | 更新 session 字段 |\n188: | Delete | 删除 session |\n189: | List (no filter) | 列出所有 session |\n190: | List (with filter) | 按 namespace/status 过滤 |\n191: | TTL 处理 | 验证过期时间设置 |\n192: | 错误处理 | 连接失败、序列化失败 |\n193: \n194: ### Integration Tests\n195: \n196: ```go\n197: func TestRedisSessionStore_Integration(t *testing.T) {\n198:     // 使用 miniredis 或真实 Redis\n199:     // 验证端到端操作\n200: }\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### Test Utilities\n204: \n205: ```go\n206: func setupTestRedis(t *testing.T) *RedisSessionStore {\n207:     // 使用 miniredis 创建测试实例\n208:     // 或连接到 test Redis\n209: }\n210: ```\n211: \n212: ## File Structure\n213: \n214: ```\n215: pkg/store/\n216:   redis.go        — RedisSessionStore 实现\n217:   redis_config.go — RedisConfig 配置\n218:   redis_test.go   — 单元测试\n219: ```\n220: \n221: ## Performance Considerations\n222: \n223: 1. **连接池**: 配置合理的 PoolSize 和 MinIdleConns\n224: 2. **Pipeline**: 批量操作时使用 Pipeline 减少 RTT\n225: 3. **序列化**: 使用 JSON 序列化，考虑 msgpack 优化\n226: 4. **过期清理**: 使用 Redis TTL 自动清理过期 session\n227: \n228: ## Configuration\n229: \n230: ### Default RedisConfig\n231: \n232: ```go\n233: var DefaultRedisConfig = &RedisConfig{\n234:     Addr:         \"localhost:6379\",\n235:     Password:     \"\",\n236:     DB:           0,\n237:     PoolSize:     10,\n238:     MinIdleConns: 5,\n239:     MaxRetries:   3,\n240:     DialTimeout:  5 * time.Second,\n241:     ReadTimeout:  3 * time.Second,\n242:     WriteTimeout: 3 * time.Second,\n243: }\n244: ```\n245: \n246: ### Environment Variables\n247: \n248: | Variable | Config Field |\n249: |----------|--------------|\n250: | REDIS_ADDR | Addr |\n251: | REDIS_PASSWORD | Password |\n252: | REDIS_DB | DB |\n253: | REDIS_POOL_SIZE | PoolSize |\n254: \n255: ## Open Questions\n256: \n257: - 是否需要支持 Redis Cluster?\n258: - 是否需要实现连接健康检查?\n259: - List 操作是否需要分页支持?\n260: - 是否需要实现批量操作 (Pipeline)?\n261: \n262: ## References\n263: \n264: - AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n265: - Redis 官方文档: https://redis.io/docs/\n266: - go-redis 文档: https://redis.uptrace.dev/\n\n(End of file - total 266 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-013 — Redis 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n实现 Redis 存储后端，提供高性能的会话持久化能力。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","time":{"start":1775857376477,"end":1775857376499}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857376513,"sessionID":"ses_286a72e99ffefKKmBHNmlIKUHY","part":{"id":"prt_d79591cbe001Prp6kT46dggVjb","messageID":"msg_d795909be001e8k5df4TKHZKme","sessionID":"ses_286a72e99ffefKKmBHNmlIKUHY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-18dad1d25447498c8135c2b3a38e75f9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package types\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"fmt\"\n5: \t\"time\"\n6: )\n7: \n8: const (\n9: \tAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n10: \tCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n11: \tSandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n12: \tSandboxClaimKind    = \"SandboxClaim\"\n13: )\n14: \n15: type CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n16: \tKind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n17: \tName      string `json:\"name\"`\n18: \tNamespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n19: }\n20: \n21: func (r *CreateSandboxRequest) Validate() error {\n22: \tif r.Kind != AgentRuntimeKind && r.Kind != CodeInterpreterKind {\n23: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"kind must be %s or %s\", AgentRuntimeKind, CodeInterpreterKind)\n24: \t}\n25: \tif r.Namespace == \"\" {\n26: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"namespace is required\")\n27: \t}\n28: \tif r.Name == \"\" {\n29: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"name is required\")\n30: \t}\n31: \treturn nil\n32: }\n33: \n34: type CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n35: \tSessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n36: \tSandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n37: \tSandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n38: \tEntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n39: }\n40: \n41: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n42: \tPath     string `json:\"path\"`\n43: \tProtocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n44: \tEndpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n45: }\n46: \n47: type SandboxInfo struct {\n48: \tKind               string              `json:\"kind\"`\n49: \tSandboxID          string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n50: \tSandboxNamespace   string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n51: \tSandboxName        string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n52: \tName               string              `json:\"name\"`\n53: \tSessionID          string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n54: \tCreatedAt          time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n55: \tExpiresAt          time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n56: \tStatus             string              `json:\"status\"`\n57: \tEntryPoints        []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n58: \tUserToken          string              `json:\"userToken,omitempty\"`\n59: \tServiceAccount     string              `json:\"serviceAccount,omitempty\"`\n60: \tServiceAccountName string              `json:\"serviceAccountName,omitempty\"`\n61: \tLastActivity       time.Time           `json:\"lastActivity,omitempty\"`\n62: }\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package types\n\nimport (\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"time\"\n)\n\nconst (\n\tAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n\tCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n\tSandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n\tSandboxClaimKind    = \"SandboxClaim\"\n)\n\ntype CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n\tKind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n\tName      string `json:\"name\"`\n\tNamespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n}\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go","time":{"start":1775857376485,"end":1775857376511}}}}
